RT @DrCatherineBall: How’s everyone feeling about the Aussie international border reopening? #australia
How’s everyone feeling about the Aussie international border reopening? #australia

I had my first interstate flight to NSW last week since June 2021. Regional city: Jetstar down and Virgin Aus back. Was pretty much business as normal apart from face-masks. But I felt less stressed as am triple vaxxed and had omicron…. And where have I put all my cotton masks!? https://t.co/fAFmDDcDaL
